## Quick rules

- Branding: always lowercase `@DISPLAY_NAME@`
- Text: ASCII-only in docs, logs, help, and code comments
- Agents work in session clones, NOT in the canonical local repo: Grok -> `~/.grok/worktrees/@PROJECT_NAME@/<session-id>/`; Claude Code -> `~/.claude/worktrees/@PROJECT_NAME@/<session-id>/`; CLI runs from `@CANONICAL_LOCAL_REPO@`
- Claude Code: NEVER edit files under `@CANONICAL_LOCAL_REPO@` -- use absolute paths to your session clone only
- New Grok session: run `scripts/init_grok_session.sh`; new Claude Code session: run `scripts/init_claude_session.sh` (see `.agentstartstack/docs/workflow.md`)
- After changes: commit in session clone; human runs `ass sync` then `git push origin main`. NEVER `git push origin` from agents (see `.agentstartstack/docs/ass.md`)

